1. *Ispitivanje* materijala je obavezno pre izrade proizvoda. (Testing of materials is mandatory before product manufacturing.)
2. Radnik je bio zadužen za *ispitivanje* kvaliteta gotovih proizvoda. (The worker was responsible for testing the quality of finished products.)
3. Prema rezultatima *ispitivanja*, konstrukcija mosta je sigurna za saobraćaj. (According to the test results, the bridge construction is safe for traffic.)
4. Na fakultetu se često organizuju razna *ispitivanja* znanja. (Various knowledge tests are often organized at the university.)
5. Inženjeri su sproveli detaljno *ispitivanje* mašine pre nego što je puštena u rad. (Engineers carried out a detailed examination of the machine before it was put into operation.)
6. Policija je provela *ispitivanje* svedoka u vezi sa ubistvom. (The police conducted an examination of witnesses regarding the murder.)
7. Kompanija je investirala u razvoj novih metoda *ispitivanja* proizvoda. (The company invested in the development of new product testing methods.)
8. Potrebno je da prođete *ispitivanje* vida pre nego što dobijete vozačku dozvolu. (You need to pass a vision test before getting a driver's license.)
9. Naučnici sprovode *ispitivanja* kako bi utvrdili uticaj novog leka na pacijente. (Scientists conduct tests to determine the effects of a new drug on patients.)
10. Rezultati *ispitivanja* su pokazali da je predloženi projekat održiv. (The test results showed that the proposed project is sustainable.)